  Jobs - Salon.com











































































































	                            Salon
	                        











































                    Jobs                






Graphic Designer – New York City
Salon Media Group (publisher of Salon.com) is hiring a full-time graphic designer with 2-3 years of experience to work in our NYC office. We are a fast-paced, high-volume, and supportive editorial environment in which editors welcome smart original ideas from one and all. We are looking for a talented professional who is pro-active, proficient, and who will enjoy coming up with editorial graphics as well as ideas for visual-based stories and series. The ideal candidate will be highly skilled in Photoshop and Illustrator. Javascript, HTML5, motion graphics and/or animation experience is a plus.
The designer will be responsible for generating artistic and eye-catching images to be used as featured images for stories on the site, as well as embedded graphics and text treatments. These will run the gamut from unique infographics and data visualizations to photo-based portraiture, all while being faithful to Salon’s voice and brand.
A link to a diverse portfolio showing a command of creative data visualization is required.
Please send application materials and LinkedIn profile to art@salon.com.







