Staff and contributors




Alex Pareene, who wrote about politics for Salon, in New York in 2012


Regular contributors include the political-opinion writers Amanda Marcotte, Scott Eric Kaufman, Heather Digby Parton, and Sean Illing, critic Andrew O'Hehir; pop-culture columnist Mary Elizabeth Williams.[citation needed]
